==Meeting the Lost Tribe==
===Greetings===
* '''Mistag:''' Who...who are you? How did you get in here?
* '''Mistag:''' Help! A surface-dweller this deep in our mines? We will all be destroyed!
* {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player performs the Goblin Bow emote:}}
** '''Mistag:''' A human knows ancient greeting?
** '''Mistag:''' Perhaps you are friend after all!
** '''Mistag:''' Greetings, friend. I am sorry I panicked when I saw you.
** '''Mistag:''' Our legends tell of the surface as a place of horror and violence, where the gods forced us to fight in terrible battles.
** '''Mistag:''' When I saw a surface-dweller appear I was afraid it was a return to the old days!
** '''Player:''' Did you break in to the castle cellar?
** '''Mistag:''' It was an accident. We were following a seam of iron and suddenly we found ourselves in a room!
** '''Mistag:''' We blocked up our tunnel behind us and ran back here. Then we did what cave goblins always do when there is a problem: we hid and hoped it would go away.
** '''Mistag:''' We meant no harm! Please tell the ruler of the above- people that we want to make peace.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player performs the Goblin Salute emote:}}
